HEADWORD: Quarreling
<hw>Quar"rel*ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Engaged in a quarrel; apt or
disposed to quarrel; <as>as, <ex>quarreling</ex> factions; a
<ex>quarreling</ex> mood.</as></def> --
<wordforms><wf>Quar"rel*ing*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

